{"tid":2466544,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"（24h運作）香港x海外谷 等緊你","createTime":"2021-03-29T07:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T17:19:28.000Z","uid":9178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cd29cd0eeb678b717717d72d464c8e46b088bf6e","tid":2466544,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-29T07:15:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"orange\">本地香港人？入！<br />\n回流香港冇耐？入！<br />\n回流香港好多年？入！<br />\n<br />\n準備移民？入！<br />\n移民多年？入！<br />\n去咗外國讀書？入！<br />\n去咗外國做嘢？入！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n本谷24h都有人喺到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為谷中包含<span class=\"red\">唔同國家</span>嘅香港人<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">好悶想識人，好悶想吹水，好悶想搵下人去街（無論外國/香港，谷友們都成功搞過聚會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span><br />\n<br />\n呢到都好啱你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n潛水請勿打擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成世唔出聚冇問題，唔出聲一定唔得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為免不停有人重填，所以set咗需要登入先填到<br />\n一星期加一次人，請耐心等候<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男女不拘 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/uuBV6d313sqkP5Z76\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FuuBV6d313sqkP5Z76&d=9FAYuqAy6z8rJZWYg5s1SIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=4af1a57d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/uuBV6d313sqkP5Z76</a>"},{"pid":"9694218ec09c05794a37c4f83687e6e8c200eb36","tid":2466544,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-29T08:51:58.000Z","msg":"唔知點解女會員多過男會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401cf4bc1a5af4d7bbf3a7a992c7f560f6578cd2","tid":2466544,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-29T10:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79761a18dda242ab09059caf1abfcc75dcaad0cc","tid":2466544,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor